OL,5, World Health Organization (WHO) staff  
OL,6, were among 83 aid workers who sexually 
OL,7, abused women and girls while tackling  
OL,8, the Ebola outbreak in the Democratic   
OL,9, Republic of Congo, a report finds.     
OL,11,FThe abuses, which included nine        
OL,12,Fallegations of rape, were committed by 
OL,13,Fboth national and international workers
OL,14,Fbetween 2018 and 2020.                 
OL,16,FThe report comes after more than 50    
OL,17,Flocal women reported sexual abuse.     
OL,19,FWHO Director-General Tedros Adhanom    
OL,20,FGhebreyesus said it was "inexcusable". 
